Features:
    User registration/login
    Profile
        Profile picture
        Tabs:
            Info - about and interests section
            PDFs/Audiobooks - list of PDFs and audiobooks
                Paginated
                Sortable (alphabetical and date added)
                Search?
                Format: Title         PDF/audiobook/play button icons
    Convert pdf (limit size) to audiobook (.mp3)
    Play audiobook
        Continue playing from where user left off

Pages:
    Home
    Register/Login (or make it a modal)
    Confirm account
    Reset Password
    Profile
    Edit Profile
    
Models:
    class Profile(models.Model):
        user = models.OneToOneField(User, on_delete=models.CASCADE)
        img = models.ImageField(upload_to='userimg/', default='userimg/avatar.png')
        bio = models.TextField(max_length=300)
        interest = models.ArrayField(
            models.TextField(max_length=100),
            size=10
        )
        created_at = models.DateTimeField(auto_now=True)
        updated_at = models.DateTimeField(auto_now=True)
        books = models.ForeignKey(Book, on_delete=models.CASCADE, null=True, blank=True)
    class Book(models.Model):
        pdf = models.ImageField(upload_to='pdf')
        audiobook = models.FileField(upload_to='audiobooks')
        last_read_time = models.FloatField()
        created_at = models.DateTimeField(auto_now=True)
        updated_at = models.DateTimeField(auto_now=True)

